就影相擺上黎<br />\n<br />\n報埋時間 地點"},{"pid":"05809f480d92e69d88c40c1acb5efbc0004f3a8e","tid":1800930,"uid":334720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:18:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>SHOP商場戰略檢討與重點</ins></strong></span> 幫手share<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong>1) 落閘就目標已達成, 可以轉場</strong></ins></span><br />\n商場落閘基本上都係因為D狗入撚哂黎, 咁達成目標 無需要再屌狗同戀戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>2) 街坊被捕個時麻煩街坊咪撚係度嘈</ins></strong></span><br />\n琴日已經有幾次係因為街坊太嘈, 個街坊大聲叫都無人聽到佢講乜, 咁樣同害9自己友無分別。一陣無名無姓無資料, 係咪想人地被消失??<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>3) 回馬槍，D狗走個時唔撚好再上前</ins></strong></span><br />\n尤其是商場入面，次撚次比人回馬槍幾次。每次都捉撚左2-3個。屌狗還屌狗, 你地係後面屌就爽, 企前面既街坊就中伏。唔好再做豬隊友<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>4) 12點好撤，再留係度攬炒指數低</ins></strong></span><br />\n咁夜對政權既傷害係邊度? 個撚個都返鳩哂屋企訓教, 車又少。同玩平原戰 自殺有咩分別? 大家要記住個目標係乜野。街上又無其他路人幫你地cover, 過左12點又無車走。好似琴日MK咁, D人又話走唔撚到比狗包圍住。咪撚再要呀寶出動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">[告急] 德國人權法30號截,差22K, 用chrome簽, <br />\nchrome可以幫你翻譯做中文, <br />\n唔撚洗睇教學都識簽 洗撚睇教學咩<br />\n直接right click 轉做中文啦 好撚易之嘛</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPI26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=f48b378d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJuUQZm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJuUQZm.png&h=76bbc9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OL5471p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOL5471p.png&h=1335725b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0101e5d855ea80c9000a7bbd863058a205997c1d","tid":1800930,"uid":120